      "preBlockScreens": [
        "Let's practice the DRT.\nIgnore the conveyor and focus only on the red border signal.\n\nPress SPACEBAR as quickly as possible whenever the border flashes red.\n\nThis block will end after 60 seconds.\n\nWe recommend resting your finger on the SPACEBAR so you can press it quickly without moving your hand.\n\nIn the following block there will be eight rounds."
      ],
      "afterBlockScreens": [
          {"html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>Great job!<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/sprite/boxy_with_coin.png' alt='Boxy With Coin' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>We will now do some practice trials putting both tasks together. Use your mouse to click-and-hold on the highlighted box for {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} second) several times until it opens, and rest a finger from the other hand on the SPACEBAR. Press the SPACEBAR whenever you see the red border flash, as quickly as you can while still opening the boxes</p><p>It might feel a little tricky to do both tasks at first but we will have several rounds of practice to familiarise you with the responses. Boxy believes in you!</p>"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "label": "Practice2",
      "phase": "practice",
      "trials": 8,
      "manipulations": [
        "difficulty_practice2",
        "condition_plan"
      ],
      "afterBlockScreens": [
         {"html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>Well done!<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/sprite/boxy_point.png' alt='Boxy Pointing' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>From here on you will always complete both the detection task and the conveyor task. The conveyor will change speeds between blocks and sometimes it will be difficult to open all the boxes. You will continue to receive colour-coded feedback on your clicks. Please try your best to open as many boxes as you can within the time limit!</p><p>Remember: Opening boxes gives you coins, but boxes being destroyed results in coins being taken away!</p>"}
      ]
    },
