  "instructions": {
    "showTaskTitleCard": false,
    "showBlockLabel": false,
    "preBlockBeforeBlockIntro": true,
    "skipBeforeBlockScreensOnRepeat": true,
    "introPages": [
      {
        "html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>Welcome to the Box Task! Meet Boxy:<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/sprite/boxy.png' alt='Boxy' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>Help Boxy collect as many coins as possible from the boxes in his factory before time runs out!<p>The Goal: Open as many boxes moving along conveyor belts to earn coins.<p>Watch out for Presents - these are worth more coins!<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/brick_types.png' alt='Present vs Crate example' style='max-width: 300px; width: 100%; height: auto;'/><p>But beware: if any box reaches the furnace at the end of the line, it will get destroyed and you will lose coins.</div>"
      },
      {"html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45;'>How to Play:<p>To open a box, click-and-hold the left mouse button on the highlighted box for exactly {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} second ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms), then release.<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/sprite/boxy_with_box.png' alt='Boxy with box' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/> <img src='assets/evander-bricks/click_hold.gif' alt='mouse hold gif' style='max-height: 120px; height: 100%; width: auto;'/></p><p>The closer to exactly {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} second) you hold for, the more of the box will be removed. If you click and hold for too long or short, less of the box will be removed.<p>By working hard at estimating {bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms} ms ({bricks.completionParams.target_hold_ms / 1000} second) holds, you can clear the boxes faster and ensure you don't lose coins from boxes being destroyed.</div>"}
    ],
    "blockSummary": {
      "enabled": true,
      "at": "block_end_before_post",
      "when": {
        "isPractice": false
      },
      "title": "End of {blockLabel} of 10",
      "lines": [                                                                                                                                                                                        
      { "html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45; style='text-align:center; margin-bottom:12px''>Great work, time for a short break.<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/break_images/break{summaryIndex1}.png' style='max-width: 300px; width: 100%; height: auto; image-rendering:pixelated'; margin-top: -2px; margin-bottom: -2px; margin-left: -2px; margin-right: -2px></p><p>Your current coint balance is: {experimentPoints}.</p><p>Across the experiment you have opened {blockCleared} boxes, and let {blockDropped} boxes be destroyed.</div>" }],
      "metrics": {
        "correctField": "responseCorrect",
        "rtField": "responseRtMs"
      }
    },
    "showBlockIntro": false,
    "showBlockLabel": false,
    "endPages": { "html": "<div style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.45; style='text-align:center; margin-bottom:12px''>DO NOT CLOSE THIS WINDOW!<p><img src='assets/evander-bricks/break_images/finish_screen.png' style='max-width: 300px; width: 100%; height: auto; image-rendering:pixelated'></p><p>You helped Boxy feed his family! He is very happy.</p><p>You have now completed the experiment. Thank you very much for participating. Please read the debrief form on the next screen, then click Continue. The experiment will redirect to SONA and automatically apply your credits.</p><p>Do not close the window until you see a message from SONA that your credits have been awarded!</p>"},
